<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Document</title>
    <script>
        function change(){
            let p = document.getElementById("firstP");
            p.innerHTML="나의 <img src='media/1.png'> 강아지";
        }
    </script>
</head>
<body>
    <h3>innerHTML 활용:아래 글자에 클릭하면 예쁜 강아지가 보입니다.</h3>
    <hr>
    <p id="firstP" style="color: blue;" onclick="change()">여기에<span style="color:  red;">클릭하세요.</span></p>
</body>
</html>
